POE-Component-Client-CouchDB

Asynchronous (POE based) communication with a CouchDB, in a similar style to
Net::CouchDb.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc POE::Component::Client::CouchDB

